&lt;p&gt;这是我制作这个简易版个人主页参考的教程：&lt;a href=&quot;https://programminghistorian.org/lessons/building-static-sites-with-jekyll-github-pages&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Building a static website with Jekyll and GitHub Pages&lt;/a&gt;。下面附上一些文章内的导航链接。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://programminghistorian.org/lessons/building-static-sites-with-jekyll-github-pages#installing-dependencies-&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Installing dependencies&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://programminghistorian.org/lessons/building-static-sites-with-jekyll-github-pages#setting-up-jekyll-&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Setting up Jekyll&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;jekyll new &lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://programminghistorian.org/lessons/building-static-sites-with-jekyll-github-pages#running-a-website-locally-&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Running a website locally&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;p&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;bundle exec jekyll serve --watch&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://programminghistorian.org/lessons/building-static-sites-with-jekyll-github-pages#tweaking-the-settings-&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tweaking the settings&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://programminghistorian.org/lessons/building-static-sites-with-jekyll-github-pages#writing-pages-and-posts-&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Writing pages and posts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://programminghistorian.org/lessons/building-static-sites-with-jekyll-github-pages#hosting-on-github-pages-&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Hosting on GitHub Pages&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;p&gt;Add a new branch named &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;gh-pages&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html">好的开始是成功的一半。</summary></entry></feed>